results.name: Denominators of resistance values that can be obtained from a network of exactly 10 one-ohm resistors, but not from any network with fewer than 10 one-ohm resistors. Numerators are in A338580.
link: Hugo Pfoertner, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..2639
example: The list of the 2639 = A338197(10) resistance values, sorted by increasing size of R = A338580(n)/a(n), is [1/10, 2/17, 3/23, 3/22, 4/27, 5/33, 5/32, ..., 32/5, 33/5, 27/4, 22/3, 23/3, 17/2, 10]. There are 15 terms for which their reciprocal value is not in the sequence, given in A338601/A338602.
results.author: _Hugo Pfoertner_, Nov 06 2020
